# ==========================================
# ScanShop API 测试文件
# 使用 VSCode REST Client 插件运行
# 或者复制到 Postman 使用
# ==========================================

### 变量定义
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = 

### ========== 健康检查 ==========

### 1. 服务器健康检查
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### ========== 认证相关接口 ==========

### 2. 手机号注册
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138888",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "测试用户888"
}

### 3. 手机号登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138888",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 4. 微信小程序登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/wechat-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "test_code_12345",
  "nickname": "微信用户",
  "avatar": "https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/default.jpg"
}

### 5. 获取用户信息（需要 token）
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 更新用户信息（需要 token）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "新昵称",
  "avatar": "https://new-avatar-url.jpg"
}

### 7. 修改密码（需要 token）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/auth/password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPassword": "123456",
  "newPassword": "654321"
}

### 8. 绑定手机号（需要 token）
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/bind-phone
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13900139999",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 9. 查询余额（需要 token）
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/balance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========== 测试错误情况 ==========

### 10. 测试：手机号格式错误
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "12345",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 11. 测试：密码强度不足
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138777",
  "password": "123"
}

### 12. 测试：手机号已注册
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138888",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 13. 测试：密码错误
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138888",
  "password": "wrong_password"
}

### 14. 测试：未提供 token
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile

### 15. 测试：无效的 token
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token_string

### ========== 购物车相关接口 ==========

### 16. 获取购物车列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 17. 添加商品到购物车
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

### 18. 获取购物车数量
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart/count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 19. 更新购物车商品数量
# 替换 :id 为实际的购物车项 ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cart/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 3
}

### 20. 取消选中商品
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cart/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "selected": false
}

### 21. 全选购物车
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cart/select-all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "selected": true
}

### 22. 取消全选
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cart/select-all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "selected": false
}

### 23. 删除单个商品
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 24. 批量删除商品
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart/batch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": [1, 2, 3]
}

### 25. 清空购物车
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========== 测试错误情况（购物车） ==========

### 26. 测试：添加不存在的商品
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 99999,
  "quantity": 1
}

### 27. 测试：添加超过库存的数量
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 99999
}

### 28. 测试：未登录访问购物车
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart

### ========== 订单相关接口 ==========

### 29. 创建订单（从购物车）
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 30. 获取订单列表（分页）
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 31. 按状态筛选订单（待支付）
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders?status=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 32. 获取订单详情（替换订单ID）
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 33. 根据订单号查询
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/by-order-no/SN202512300001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 34. 获取订单统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 35. 取消订单
PUT {{baseUrl}}/orders/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========== 支付相关接口 ==========

### 36. 创建微信支付订单
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "paymentMethod": "wechat"
}

### 37. 创建余额支付订单
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "paymentMethod": "balance"
}

### 38. 模拟支付成功（开发环境）
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/mock-pay
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentNo": "PAY17035000001234"
}

### 39. 查询支付状态
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/PAY17035000001234
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 40. 微信支付回调（模拟）
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "out_trade_no": "PAY17035000001234",
  "transaction_id": "4200001234567890",
  "total_fee": 1550,
  "result_code": "SUCCESS"
}

### ========== 说明 ==========
# 使用方法：
# 1. 安装 VSCode 插件：REST Client
# 2. 点击请求上方的 "Send Request"
# 3. 查看右侧的响应结果
#
# 变量使用：
# - 修改 @baseUrl 为你的服务器地址
# - 登录后，复制返回的 token 到 @token 变量
# - 或者在每个请求中直接替换 {{token}}

